      "content": "As someone obsessed with whether AI can play D&D, I am going to have fun with the ChatGPT goblin phenomenon for a bit. You can ignore me.\n\nBut if you do want to take it seriously, here is a paper my team and I wrote about why AI playing D&D should be an AI grand challenge: arxiv.org/abs/2509.17192",
