      },
      "content": "Designating that most uses of the term \"goblin\" and \"gremlin\" are not legitimate while designating most uses of the word \"frog\" as legitimate is the imposition of a set of values on a technology. Why do a small number of people in Silicon Valley get to decide whether goblins are inappropriate?",
